rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0010
rows.name: Boy, oh, boy...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0020
rows.name: You really put me through the wringer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0030
rows.name:
Yeah, well, if you weren't organic,
it would've been a lot easier for us, too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_JNK0010
rows.name: Question

rows.label: xs31170100_SEL0010
rows.name:
Ask if he meant "organic"
as in "human body."

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0040
rows.name: Bingo.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0050
rows.name: Al's no mim—just good old blood and bones.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_JNK0020
rows.name: Nitpick

rows.label: xs31170100_SEL0020
rows.name:
Point out that mims aren't
technically biological.

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0060
rows.name: Right.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0070
rows.name: Difference is, Al isn't a mim—it's his real body.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0090
rows.name:
You thought all crew members were
supposed to be mims, didn't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0100
rows.name: But you see,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0105
rows.name: Al here might just be the "chosen one."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0110
rows.name: The Ares Prime...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0120
rows.name: needs a warm body to run.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0130
rows.name: Guys...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0140
rows.name: Does this matter right now...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0150
rows.name: You're right. But first—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0160
rows.name: It's good to have you back, Al.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0170
rows.name:
The hero returns,
and with him our hearts are all uplifted.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0190
rows.name: Do me a favor and nix the "hero" thing?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0200
rows.name: It's weird being put on a pedestal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0210
rows.name: ...Anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0220
rows.name: Can I get a recap? I've missed a lot of scuttlebutt.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0230
rows.name: I'm like a lost time traveler here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0240
rows.name: Certainly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0250
rows.name: Let me give you the bullet points.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0260
rows.name: ...Okay, wow.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0270
rows.name:
You guys sure had a rough time
while I was away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0280
rows.name: All right then...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0290
rows.name: Now I'd like to ask you some questions.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0300
rows.name: Al,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0310
rows.name: where were you, up until now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0320
rows.name: To explain that part,[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0330
rows.name: I'll need the results of my Skell's analysis.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0340
rows.name:
You'll never believe me unless I give you
something to back it up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0350
rows.name: What are you trying to say?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0390
rows.name:
We've detected a giant energy surge
in the vicinity of Sylvalum.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0400
rows.name: A de-mat event?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0410
rows.name: No.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0420
rows.name: It's not a pattern we've observed before, sir.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0430
rows.name: Tch...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0440
rows.name: Just one thing after the next here...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs31170100_MSG0450
rows.name: Put it on screen.[ST:wait ]
